dn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031420_3734190120204984_7048526618196222799_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=f0P0BdeB1coQ7kNvgEEduJa&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDCtN07q3MHwZ1wyN6yV6_Bo1txZnYlKN2c0BwUtHYCVw&oe=676FF889"}, "display_name": "Sky Runner", "keywords": ["Drone", "RC", "FPV", "Christmas", "Holiday"], "long_description": "# Make an Impact!\nFrom December 18, 2024, through January 28, 2025, players can experience Gift Drift, a festive new game mode where holiday-themed drones deliver presents while avoiding lumps of coal. However, the stakes here are quite real\u2014every successful delivery in-game makes a notable real-world impact. Learn more by checking out our socials.\n\n{596157746283278}\n\n# Take Control of the Skies and Save the City!\n\nSky Runner allows you to experience the thrills of flying a drone without the need of expensive equipment. \n\n{1306304820389672}\n\nFly drones wherever you want in your living room, your backyard \u2013 even in your bathroom! \n\nCreate your own courses, and race to the finish.\n{608471388195720}\n\nMore scenarios will be added in the future, and we are looking for YOUR feedback. Join the Flat2VR Discord to share your ideas directly with the devs! \nhttps://discord.gg/yC5498Jd4B", "short_description": "Transform your living room into a high-stakes battleground with Sky Runner, the next level in mixed-reality drone combat.\n\n"}]}, "developer_name": "RudyAA", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.bomberdronevr.com/privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Flat2VR Studios", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://bomberdronevr.com/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "331529188132278"}, {"id": "1990104051447093"}, {"id": "459781504968480"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", 